{"tid":15603,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[劏雞]小提琴cover廣東歌","createTime":"2016-12-01T05:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T09:51:56.000Z","uid":48488,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dc5c5e69f3adb866ca9a2d385cf6ca276d77fec0","tid":15603,"uid":48488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:17:41.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲好，細佬我就玩左一輪劏雞，希望打啲譜同拍片俾大家參考下，希望為香港出一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定期出野，大想聽咩歌/要咩譜都可以出聲，盡量滿足大家要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n片: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=209108736202050&amp;id=204052133374377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D209108736202050%26id%3D204052133374377&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=1379cb0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=209108736202050&amp;id=204052133374377</a><br />\n<br />\n我成日都諗，點解要逼啲學生學classical呢? 明明啲學生成日自己印啲流行曲譜黎玩，人地又無諗住讀音樂，做小提琴家。所以今次我想將一啲我鍾意嘅流行曲打成譜，連埋歌詞，俾大家download黎用，順勢拍埋片做參考。拉就拉得麻麻地，不過每首歌我都有用心諗住歌詞黎拉，希望唔會太難聽。走音就在所難免，人地又唔係大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲人成日講，&ldquo;哎呀依家啲人重詞多過音樂㗎喇~&rdquo; 咁點解唔搵個方法等人欣賞晒兩樣呢? 睇片啦，旋律由我拉，歌詞由你再用心咀嚼! 抵玩哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n剪片錄音我全部都未試過，真係玩死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望表達到首歌嘅感覺啦，用心聽，隱約仲會聽到啲歌詞㗎(因為我唔識清vocal清得好啲)。<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b3fd3b31b6a407fa6ab9dd70d20783bf7f4168","tid":15603,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:38:19.000Z","msg":"小提琴友廣東歌友留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇興趣一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93789b226076bc4a756bd8c9bfeb633b73b9cfaa","tid":15603,"uid":30358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T09:46:01.000Z","msg":"巴打正啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都唔鍾意拉古典歌<br />\n希望將來整多d流行歌譜黎拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7696517e4e42263abdccb655fb2ce914d603b217","tid":15603,"uid":33313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:18:41.000Z","msg":"小提琴撚留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f515aae2d9c4d02a4c1bbf2c860024434cad028f","tid":15603,"uid":48488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:52:57.000Z","msg":"好感動呀有人回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f5cddc829496242d8c909b78105126a4702788","tid":15603,"uid":48488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:53:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小提琴友廣東歌友留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇興趣一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一齊拍片俾人公審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693381651b20e19635c30cd0e19b526bc4bd7fc1","tid":15603,"uid":48488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:54:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打正啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都唔鍾意拉古典歌<br />\n希望將來整多d流行歌譜黎拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"h